title: Dzmitry Kalachow
text:
Dzmitry Kalachow (; ; born 16 June 1978) is a retired <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er.
He is the older brother of the Belarusian international <a href="Timofei%20Kalachev">Timofei Kalachev</a>.
Honours.
Dnepr-Transmash Mogilev
Dinamo Minsk
Dinamo Brest
